{"tid":744764,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"點解酒越飲越暖，水越飲越寒？","createTime":"2018-07-16T07:42:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-19T07:11:49.000Z","uid":165024,"like":86,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"b9b9d3726d6110df1f7027ca7d9fb3e1aa6022b1","tid":744764,"uid":165024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T07:42:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/16/154148_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F16%2F154148_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=a3ccbc2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<code>「首先酒裡的酒精被身體吸收以後，能刺激體表的血管，使其變粗，血流加快，內臟的血液也流到體表並向外發散熱量。由於血液是熱的，大量的血液流向體表以後，使人身上暫時感到熱乎乎的，所以說酒越喝越暖。但這對防止熱量向外散發是非常不利的。因為喝酒後擴張的血管不能靈敏地收縮變細來防止血液向外散發熱量，於是身體中的熱量丟失很多，一旦冷上來就會抖的停不下來。這也是喝完酒以後先熱後冷的道理。水喝多了會排汗，也會導致人體熱量散失，若喝涼水還有涼血的作用，所以說水越喝越寒。」</code>"},{"pid":"e9e23d6b69205f1351c86175ea4b41d8b2b258bf","tid":744764,"uid":179571,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T07:43:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"05b804f0c90b5fcc2b48dca6a04c94ef7bfb59a6","tid":744764,"uid":138138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T07:43:32.000Z","msg":"勁"},{"pid":"b34972a55d3b36d895656ed1c23eaa3376f49f0a","tid":744764,"uid":41737,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T07:43:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"05fd0640e9d5f3b2466c3ccb164f5eca1854491e","tid":744764,"uid":165024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9e23d6b69205f1351c86175ea4b41d8b2b258bf","tid":744764,"uid":179571,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T07:43:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T07:44:59.000Z","msg":"可愛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15c2117e1cb6a9af150126147d83c605a3eaecd2","tid":744764,"uid":165024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05b804f0c90b5fcc2b48dca6a04c94e